      "span_text": "The microencapsulation efficiency could be increased considerably from 56% at C o = 0 to 88% at C o = 10 wt% due to the increase in the viscosity of shell solution and the mean diameter, especially due to the increase in the dispersing stability of SHC in the shell material solution by the help of PR-300  [24].",
